<view class="page data-v-22dcc176"><view class="nav data-v-22dcc176"><label class="back-btn data-v-22dcc176" bindtap="{{a}}">←</label> 问答详情 </view><view class="qa-detail-content data-v-22dcc176"><view class="qa-detail-question data-v-22dcc176"><view class="qa-detail-question-title data-v-22dcc176">秦始皇兵马俑需要提前预约吗？有线下售票窗口吗？</view><view class="qa-detail-question-meta data-v-22dcc176"><label class="qa-detail-question-time data-v-22dcc176">2026-0X-0X</label><label class="qa-detail-question-tags data-v-22dcc176"><label class="qa-detail-question-tag data-v-22dcc176">门票信息</label><label class="qa-detail-question-tag data-v-22dcc176">西安</label></label></view></view><view class="qa-detail-answer data-v-22dcc176"><view class="qa-detail-answer-header data-v-22dcc176"><view class="qa-detail-answer-avatar data-v-22dcc176"><image class="data-v-22dcc176" src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=professional%20guide%20portrait%20friendly%20smile&image_size=square" alt="回答者头像"/></view><view class="qa-detail-answer-info data-v-22dcc176"><view class="qa-detail-answer-name data-v-22dcc176">西安老陕</view><view class="qa-detail-answer-badge data-v-22dcc176">本地达人</view></view><view class="qa-detail-answer-time data-v-22dcc176">2026-0X-0X 10:25</view></view><view class="qa-detail-answer-content data-v-22dcc176"><view class="data-v-22dcc176">有线下售票窗口！</view><view class="data-v-22dcc176">预约方式：关注「秦始皇兵马俑博物馆」官方公众号，提前1-3天预约门票。节假日、周末一定要尽早预约，否则很容易没票。</view><view class="data-v-22dcc176">门票价格：成人120元，学生半价，65岁以上老人免票。</view></view></view><view class="qa-detail-follow-up data-v-22dcc176"><view class="qa-detail-follow-up-title data-v-22dcc176">游客补充追问</view><view class="qa-detail-follow-up-question data-v-22dcc176"><view class="qa-detail-follow-up-question-header data-v-22dcc176"><view class="qa-detail-follow-up-question-avatar data-v-22dcc176"><image class="data-v-22dcc176" src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=tourist%20portrait%20friendly%20smile&imag